🚨Huda Beauty Purple Haze VS Nicka K Sugar Plum 🚨
.
➡️ Huda Beauty & Nicka K both aren’t 100% dupes but there are 5 similar shades which you can find in Nicka K 
➡️ Pigmentation wise Huda Beauty is more pigmented than Nicka K 
➡️ Although the Pigment seems less in Nicka K , you can use hacks such as using setting sprays & concealer to bring out the POP effect in the shimmers
➡️ Both the eyeshadows blend amazingly with each other , there’s no problem in making the mattes & shimmers work together 
➡️ Affordability is subjective to each & everyone 
➡️ If you think you can want to use more purples and pinks then Nicka K one is for you! 
➡️ Packaging differs as the price point of both is different , however both are easy to carry & compact! 
.
